SubjectOrder Transferring the Administration of Real Property to the Canadian High Arctic Research Station
PrecisOrder (1) amending Order in Council P.C. 2015-0316 of March 12, 2015; and (2) transferring from the Minister of Northern Affairs to the Canadian High Arctic Research Station the administration of the real property located in the town of Cambridge Bay, Nunavut.
